record.title: DISPENSING WITH CALENDAR WEDNESDAY BUSINESS ON TOMORROW
record.narrative:
DISPENSING WITH CALENDAR WEDNESDAY BUSINESS ON TOMORROW -- (House of Representatives - January 15, 2008)

[Page: H4]

speaking.paragraph: Madam Speaker, I ask unanimous consent that the business in order under the Calendar Wednesday rule be dispensed with tomorrow.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Maryland?
